Package: MDP2
Type: Package
Title: Markov Decision Processes (MDPs) in R
Description: Using this package you can create and optimize (semi) MDPs with
    discrete time steps and state space. Both hierarchical and ordinary-traditional
    MDPs can be modelled.
Version: 2.0.0
Date: 2013-08-15
